-# Alternate buttons

%h4 Alternate Buttons
%p Alternate buttons are identified with the <code>.btn-alt</code> class. They should only be used on a colored background and do not include any disabled styles. These buttons are meant to be a primary call to action.

.sg-alt-btns

  %a.btn-alt.btn-large(href="#") Alternate Button
  %a.btn-alt(href="#") Alternate Button
  %a.btn-alt.btn-small(href="#") Alternate Button
